          <title>Athletics agree to $60M, 5-year contract with slugger Brent Rooker, AP source says</title>
          <description><![CDATA[(AP) -- The Athletics have agreed to a $60 million, five-year contract with slugger Brent Rooker, a person familiar with the negotiations told The Associated Press on Monday night. The person spoke on condition of anonymity because the agreement had not been announced.]]></description>
